Information on how to use the documents in this folder.
#######################################################

### Illumina_Guided_HP_FMR1_and_HTT_2.sh & SNV_Base_Identification2.py
Is run in terminal by calling 'bash Illumina_Guided_HP_FMR1_and_HTT_2.sh'.
This script calls SNV_Base_Identification2.py.
The output is data frames with ONT read-IDs as rows and Illumina SNV positions as columns. The dataframe is filled with bases (A,T,C,G).

### phasing_nanopore_reads_HC_gowers_dist_R.r
The dataframes from above are being used to phase the reads into two haplotypes.

